On November 6, 2004, the mother of Robson dos Santos, or Robinho, was kidnapped. On , the mother of Brazilian soccer player Luis Fabiano was kidnapped by criminals, also in Campinas. The mother of Fabiano is still missing. The other hostages were released and are well.

